        <svg class="accordion-chevron w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" id="chevron6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-body" id="body6">
        <div class="px-5 pb-6 pt-2 border-t border-gray-100">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-cenoa-dark mb-2 text-base">The Rule</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">At least <strong>80% of your foreign export earnings</strong> must enter Pakistan through official banking channels each fiscal year (July 1 – June 30).</p>

          <h4 class="font-bold text-cenoa-dark mb-2 text-base">What Counts as "Repatriated"</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1.5 mb-4 ml-4">
            <li>✅ Payoneer withdrawal to Pakistani bank</li>
            <li>✅ Wire transfer to Pakistani bank</li>
            <li>✅ Money in your ESFCA (foreign currency account in Pakistan)</li>
            <li>❌ Money sitting in Payoneer balance</li>
            <li>❌ Money spent directly from Payoneer card (outside Pakistan)</li>
            <li>❌ Money kept in Wise balance</li>
            <li>⚠️ Wise transfer to Pakistani bank (may not be classified correctly)</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="warning-box mb-4">
            <strong>⚠️ What happens if you fail:</strong> Your entire income gets reclassified from "IT export" to "regular business income." Tax goes from 0.25% to progressive rates up to <strong>45%</strong>. The government can apply this retroactively.
          </div>

          <!-- Interactive 80% Repatriation Tracker -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 mt-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-cenoa-dark mb-1 text-base">📊 Your 80% Repatriation Tracker</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-4">Fiscal year: July 1 – June 30 · Data stored locally on your device only.</p>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <label class="calc-label" for="repTotal">Total earned from foreign clients this fiscal year ($)</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <span class="input-prefix font-bold">$</span>
                  <input type="number" id="repTotal" class="calc-input pl-8" placeholder="0" min="0" step="100" value="" oninput="calculateRepatriation()" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="calc-label" for="repBank">Total withdrawn/transferred to Pakistani bank ($)</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <span class="input-prefix font-bold">$</span>
                  <input type="number" id="repBank" class="calc-input pl-8" placeholder="0" min="0" step="100" value="" oninput="calculateRepatriation()" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="calc-label" for="repESFCA">Currently in ESFCA ($)</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <span class="input-prefix font-bold">$</span>
                  <input type="number" id="repESFCA" class="calc-input pl-8" placeholder="0" min="0" step="100" value="" oninput="calculateRepatriation()" />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Results -->
            <div class="mt-5 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Total Repatriated:</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-bold text-cenoa-dark" id="repRepatriated">$0</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700">Repatriation Percentage:</span>
                <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold" id="repPercentage" style="color: #6b7280;">0%</span>
              </div>

              <!-- Visual Gauge -->
              <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-6 overflow-hidden relative">
                  <div id="repGauge" class="gauge-fill h-full rounded-full" style="width: 0%; background-color: #ef4444;"></div>
                  <!-- 80% marker -->
                  <div class="absolute top-0 h-full border-l-2 border-dashed border-gray-600" style="left: 80%;">
                    <span class="absolute -top-5 -left-3 text-xs text-gray-600 font-bold">80%</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">
                  <span>0%</span>
                  <span class="text-red-500 font-semibold">← Danger zone</span>
                  <span>80%</span>
                  <span class="text-green-500 font-semibold">Safe →</span>
                  <span>100%</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Status message -->
              <div id="repMessage" class="text-sm font-semibold p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-center">
                Enter your amounts above to track your repatriation status.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

